Package com.adobe.xfa.text.markup

Class MarkupIn

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.xfa.text.markup.MarkupIn
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MarkupEngineIn
    public abstract class MarkupIn
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides common base class support for input markup engines. It caches a pointer to the markup target (class TextMkBase) and provides a simple set of methods that the input engine can call to build up the rich text.

    For more information, please see the extenral documentation.
